{"tid":1499232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 世山單車舖藍屍老細襲擊義士","createTime":"2019-08-23T15:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T18:01:32.000Z","uid":92339,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b6133d8ec8496a9bc337a8cb0e2bc73078a9aa","tid":1499232,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:53:40.000Z","msg":"轉自 香港突發事故報料區<br />\n8月23日 2250<br />\n有藍絲癲佬搶人把長遮 ,係咁打人個頭, 打咗多下 ,打到傘都斷埋。重揼咗一男一女 受害人 眼鏡落河, 揼埋手機落河😠<br />\n<br />\n剛才行返屋企途中沿 太和 林村河，見到一單打人案。有一對夫婦30歲，回應對面河的人講光復香港，時代革命，比後面一個唔識嘅 40多歲 男人鬧佢是否發緊夢。<br />\n跟住佢哋冇理，個男人又追住， 受害人 說了關你咩事，個惡人就打個男人個頭好多下，搶咗事主把遮打到遮都斷埋，個女仔即刻用電話拍，個男人就搶個女仔嘅眼鏡同埋電話抌咗落河。好彩有街坊見到制服咗個男仔，跟住就call警車同埋十字車。<br />\n#藍絲癲佬係世山單車舖老細<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2219456438181556/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2219456438181556%2F&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6ouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=01976525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2219456438181556/</a>"},{"pid":"507f6f68f0af52d4b404944a12716e308ac9a7b6","tid":1499232,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb0fe9ed6e46bd8e7310c9d3ae268a34c74a466f","tid":1499232,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90f80a156134ead3a434798b05371aa4c1b23728","tid":1499232,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74dc7ab94bf3c99fe035173520a539193cfe4021","tid":1499232,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8841faceb290aaa84937e39358ca0344b1f3394","tid":1499232,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:57:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8d5aeb865eb8a6881332819b4417fd8